---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cool Stuff I Made — Rian" description="Interactive visualizations and simulations from engineering projects.">
  <h1>Cool Stuff I Made</h1>

  <section class="project">
    <h2>How long until the pizza is ready to eat?</h2>
    <p class="project-meta">CFD study · OpenFOAM · Fluid Mechanics I</p>
    <a href="/cool-stuff/pizza-cfd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <img src="/images/cool-stuff/pizza-cfd.png" alt="Pizza cooling CFD visualization" loading="lazy" />
    </a>
    <p class="open-link"><a href="/cool-stuff/pizza-cfd.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open the interactive visualization →</a></p>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor
      incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis
      nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="project">
    <h2>Stress State Visualizer</h2>
    <p class="project-meta">Interactive 3D · three.js · Solid Mechanics</p>
    <iframe src="/cool-stuff/stress-visualizer.html" title="Stress state visualizer" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    <p class="open-link"><a href="/cool-stuff/stress-visualizer.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open full screen →</a></p>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis aute irure dolor
      in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="project">
    <h2>N · V · M Diagrams</h2>
    <p class="project-meta">Internal forces in beams · Solid Mechanics</p>
    <iframe src="/cool-stuff/nvm-diagrams.html" title="Beam internal force diagrams" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    <p class="open-link"><a href="/cool-stuff/nvm-diagrams.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open full screen →</a></p>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Excepteur sint occaecat
      cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.
    </p>
    <div class="image-pair">
      <img src="/images/cool-stuff/distribuicao-tensoes.png" alt="Stress distribution in a beam cross-section" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/images/cool-stuff/empenamento.png" alt="Cross-section warping visualization" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ut perspiciatis unde
      omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="project">
    <h2>Rocket Flight Simulation</h2>
    <p class="project-meta">3DOF / 6DOF flight dynamics · Python · INVICTUS II</p>
    <img src="/images/cool-stuff/rocket-3dof.png" alt="3DOF rocket trajectory simulation" loading="lazy" />
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nemo enim ipsam
      voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur
      magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-block: var(--space-8) var(--space-12);
  }

  .project {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .project h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .project-meta {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .project p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .project img {
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .project iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 480px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #ddd);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .open-link {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .image-pair {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-block: var(--space-4);
  }

  .image-pair img {
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .image-pair {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
